---
import videoSrc from "../assets/placeholder-bg.mp4";
---

<video
  autoplay
  loop
  muted
  class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-full brightness-50 grayscale object-cover"
>
  <source src={videoSrc} type="video/mp4" />
  Your browser does not support the video tag.
</video>
<div
  class="relative flex flex-col lg:flex-row w-full h-screen justify-end lg:justify-start items-center text-white min-h-screen px-8 py-8"
>
  <div class="flex flex-col gap-12 lg:gap-24 lg:w-2/3">
    <div
      class="flex flex-col gap-2 md:gap-4 font-cormorand text-center lg:text-start uppercase"
    >
      <h1
        class="text-5xl md:text-8xl xl:text-9xl font-medium xl:leading-32 2xl:leading-30"
      >
        Lucca Romaniello
      </h1>
      <h2 class="text-base xl:text-2xl font-satoshi leading-snug font-light">
        Full Stack Engineer with product design background
      </h2>
    </div>
    <div
      class="flex flex-col gap-2 leading-relaxed text-center lg:text-start xl:text-xl font-light 2xl:pr-24"
    >
      <p>
        Blending engineering expertise and design sensibility across startups
        and global teams for 6+ years.
      </p>
      <p>
        Based in Brazil, working globally. Open to full-time and freelance
        opportunities.
      </p>
      <video
        autoplay
        muted
        width="320"
        height="240"
        class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-full brightness-20 grayscale"
      >
        <source src="../assets/placeholder-bg.mp4" type="video/mp4" />
        Your browser does not support the video tag.
      </video>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="order-first lg:order-none">
    <p class="font-caveat text-2xl text-center">
      On most days, you’ll find me with some <em>pão de queijo</em> and a cup of
      black coffee. No sugar.
    </p>
  </div>
</div>

<style>
  img.background {
    background-image: url("../assets/bg.jpg");
  }
</style>
